{"title":"夜宿林场","authors":["梁上泉"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":10,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜宿林场"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梁上泉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日登鸡子顶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜宿场长家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家在森林深处，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"板房檐上开野花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"主人烧火炉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炉边煨青茶；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"主人点松明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明子爆金花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"微光照笑脸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"细细把话拉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"传说此山似金鸡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸡鸣满天霞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只恨白军来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乱把树木砍伐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸡身毛秃尽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从此成了个哑吧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谈到公社办林场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叹息变为一串哈哈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他取出林木标本，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫我一一细看它。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有桑有桐有果树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有松有柏有云杉……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿色的金子呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多得竞放光华！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当夜做了个好梦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦见山石发青丫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金鸡又长满彩羽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"振翅啼醒十万家！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}